topic.body: can never have babies, so why are people referring to them as 'She/her?'

1514848604_16NS3rBdW9zpLmLSQoD8nLTtNVsRF.body: Why do you insist on being addressed as "Her" when you can't have babies?  This makes no sense.  It is non-sense to me.  Complete and utter Nonsense.
